desc.en: Bet500.ONE is a blockchain game experiment platform developed by 5 million lottery network. Based on the EOS public chain development, Bet500.ONE is an experimental development of a series of blockchain quiz games, such as digital color games, competitive games, and team games.
desc.zh: Bet500.ONE是由500万彩票网策划开发的区块链游戏实验平台。Bet500.ONE基于EOS公链开发，围绕数字彩类游戏、竞技类游戏、团队类游戏等一系列区块链竞猜游戏进行实验化拓展。
